data.description: Situated in the scenic surroundings of Knoxville, TN, this spacious 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home boasts both charm and potential. A welcoming carport leads to the home's entrance, complemented by a generous front deck, perfect for soaking in those Tennessee sunsets. Set on an expansive lot, the property ensures privacy and ample outdoor space for recreation or landscaping dreams. Inside, the home unfolds over two levels, with a fully finished lower level offering additional living or entertainment space. Modern stainless appliances in the kitchen ensure functionality meets style.
